" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印就要由佢唔生之後先慢慢退，<br />\n嗰時醫生打咗個比喻，話生暗瘡好似山火咁，<br />\n一日仲燒緊啲樹木都生唔返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然平時好多人話食A酸好差點點點，<br />\n但我唯一後悔嘅係我太遲先決定去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後就係，巴打total預一皮到啦，早日康覆呀喂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7fe0d87446a273831a6852baeaf23f50164d3c","tid":49110,"uid":3469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T06:43:35.000Z","msg":"如果已經成面都洞口，點解決？<br />\n唔好答我整容同自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f656b1efb27a304da1f8c9a65f613ee021d94cb","tid":49110,"uid":71768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T06:46:18.000Z","msg":"啲人話早晚食奇異果會好啲<br />\n<br />\n我唔敢食a酸 因為要驗血 <br />\n<br />\n試下奇異果 食1個月到啲印會慢慢退"},{"pid":"31923c47fd6dc6db2f94c8176e2ccb0833e87e8d","tid":49110,"uid":5372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-11T06:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>btw我睇柴灣朱，我覺得幾好，佢好好心機解釋我聽又唔嫌我煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你預一開頭食嘅第一個月内會爆，爆到兩個星期到就會完，<br />\n神奇嘅事就會開始發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印就要由佢唔生之後先慢慢退，<br />\n嗰時醫生打咗個比喻，話生暗瘡好似山火咁，<br />\n一日仲燒緊啲樹木都生唔返出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然平時好多人話食A酸好差點點點，<br />\n但我唯一後悔嘅係我太遲先決定去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後就係，巴打total預一皮到啦，早日康覆呀喂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n朱除左開A酸俾你,仲有冇開埋抗生素俾你頂下個爆發期呀?<br />\n一個月幾錢 同埋食幾多MG<br />\n我打過去問姑娘,姑娘話每次見醫生覆診都要$250..<br />\n但A酸幾錢就唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}